-- Victoria’s Secret Owner May Buy La Senza Brand, Times Reports
-- B y   M a t h e w   C a r r
-- 2011-12-18T11:22:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-18/victoria-s-secret-owner-may-buy-la-senza-brand-times-reports.html
Limited Brands Inc., which owns
Victoria’s Secret lingerie chain, may be close to buying the La
Senza Plc brand, the  Sunday Times reported , without saying where
it obtained the information.  Limited is not interested in buying Ilford, England-based
La Senza’s 158 shops, putting 2,600 jobs at risk, the newspaper
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mathew Carr in London at 
